Tech Talent

We're rethinking technology to build a better Society

You want to be part of an organisation that isn’t just about the bottom line. You want development, support and benefits to build your career on. And you want the kind of challenges that will stretch and test you. That’s us.


We’re serious about making technology faster and simpler for our 15 million members. And backed by a multi-billion tech investment, we’re hiring people with the talent and drive to help us succeed.


We'll be moving into our new location at the iconic Post Building in Holborn, London early in 2020. Our head office will remain in Swindon but we know Holborn is a great place to attract industry-leading talent within the Fintech capital of the world. 

Our new base will house around 1000 colleagues and a new digital and data innovation centre for those working in Digital, Data, Engineering, Architecture, Development Ops and Design specialisms. 


We're actively recruiting hundreds of digital and technology roles into London now and over the coming months.


If you'd like to move with us, click here to register for our talent pool or see below to find vacancies in your area of expertise.
